00:08.275 --> 00:10.975
I was wrong to,

00:11.546 --> 00:15.621
think that this was going
to be a happy house.

00:15.622 --> 00:20.602
Once we got on to the
road, everything changed.

00:25.586 --> 00:30.206
How do you battle something you can't see?

00:33.201 --> 00:36.681
I don't believe in ghosts.

00:36.908 --> 00:39.488
But I do now.

00:40.857 --> 00:44.277
It's not humanly possible.

00:44.361 --> 00:47.061
Mom! Go, go go!

00:47.374 --> 00:51.154
I was going to die that night.

00:51.427 --> 00:53.391
And all I could think was..

00:53.392 --> 00:57.232
My daughter's going to die too?

